    "Connect over the device's transport (BLE for Ledger and Trezor; NFC or USB-C for YubiKey) so Maknoon can read its serial. The device does not need to be promoted into Identity or any network yet, that happens in a separate step." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "اتصل عبر ناقل الجهاز (BLE لـ Ledger و Trezor، NFC أو USB-C لـ YubiKey) ليتمكن Maknoon من قراءة الرقم التسلسلي. لا يحتاج الجهاز إلى الترقية إلى الهوية أو أي شبكة بعد، فذلك يحدث في خطوة منفصلة."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Connect over the device's transport (BLE for Ledger and Trezor; NFC or USB-C for YubiKey) so Maknoon can read its serial. The device does not need to be promoted into Identity or any network yet, that happens in a separate step."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "通过设备对应的传输方式连接（Ledger 与 Trezor 使用 BLE，YubiKey 使用 NFC 或 USB-C），以便 Maknoon 读取其序列号。此时无需将设备提升为身份设备或加入任何网络，这些将在后续单独的步骤中完成。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
