    "Enabling / disabling runs FIDO2 hmac-secret enrollment over the device's existing transport. Only YubiKey enrollment needs the paid Apple Developer Program (NFC reader + accessory entitlements). Ledger and Trezor run over Bluetooth and do not need any additional iOS entitlements." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "يقوم التفعيل/التعطيل بتشغيل تسجيل FIDO2 hmac-secret عبر الناقل الحالي للجهاز. تسجيل YubiKey فقط يحتاج إلى برنامج Apple Developer المدفوع (قارئ NFC + استحقاقات الملحقات). Ledger و Trezor يعملان عبر Bluetooth ولا يحتاجان إلى أي استحقاقات iOS إضافية."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Enabling / disabling runs FIDO2 hmac-secret enrollment over the device's existing transport. Only YubiKey enrollment needs the paid Apple Developer Program (NFC reader + accessory entitlements). Ledger and Trezor run over Bluetooth and do not need any additional iOS entitlements."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "启用或停用会通过设备现有的传输方式执行 FIDO2 hmac-secret 注册。只有 YubiKey 注册需要付费的 Apple Developer Program（NFC 读取器与配件权限）。Ledger 和 Trezor 通过蓝牙运行，无需任何额外的 iOS 权限。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Enabling a device wraps your BIP39 entropy with an AES-256 key derived from a deterministic signature only that device can produce. The device is required on every cold launch unlock once enabled. Losing the device strands the sandwich; restore from your 24-word paper seed in that case." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "تفعيل الجهاز يغلّف إنتروبيا BIP39 الخاصة بك بمفتاح AES-256 مشتق من توقيع حتمي لا يستطيع إنتاجه سوى ذلك الجهاز. يصبح الجهاز مطلوباً عند كل فك قفل بعد التشغيل البارد بمجرد تفعيله. فقدان الجهاز يعزل Sandwich، استعد عبر بذرة الورق المكونة من 24 كلمة في تلك الحالة."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Enabling a device wraps your BIP39 entropy with an AES-256 key derived from a deterministic signature only that device can produce. The device is required on every cold launch unlock once enabled. Losing the device strands the sandwich; restore from your 24-word paper seed in that case."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "启用某个设备时，会用一个 AES-256 密钥封装您的 BIP39 熵，该密钥由仅该设备能产生的确定性签名派生而来。启用后，每次冷启动解锁都需要该设备。若设备丢失，三明治将无法解锁，需要使用您的 24 个纸质助记词恢复。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Enabling Lockdown now will permanently remove the Show recovery phrase option from this device. You can still present credentials and use the wallet normally, you just cannot view the recovery phrase on this device anymore." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "تفعيل الإغلاق التام الآن سيزيل دائماً خيار عرض عبارة الاسترداد من هذا الجهاز. لا يزال بإمكانك تقديم بيانات الاعتماد واستخدام المحفظة بشكل طبيعي، لكنك لن تستطيع عرض عبارة الاسترداد على هذا الجهاز بعد الآن."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Enabling Lockdown now will permanently remove the Show recovery phrase option from this device. You can still present credentials and use the wallet normally, you just cannot view the recovery phrase on this device anymore."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "立即启用锁定模式将永久移除此设备上的“显示助记词”选项。您仍可正常使用钱包和出示凭据，只是再也无法在此设备上查看助记词。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Enabling Lockdown removes the ability to view your recovery phrase on this device. After this, the only ways to recover your identity are:" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "تفعيل الإغلاق التام يزيل القدرة على عرض عبارة الاسترداد على هذا الجهاز. بعد ذلك، الطرق الوحيدة لاسترداد هويتك هي:"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Enabling Lockdown removes the ability to view your recovery phrase on this device. After this, the only ways to recover your identity are:"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "启用锁定模式将禁用在此设备上查看助记词的能力。之后恢复身份的唯一方式是："
          }
        }
      }
    },
