    "Ethereum + ERC-20 support is on the roadmap. Maknoon already handles the Identity Sandwich's walletControlEth credential, but the read-only chain wallet (balance + tx history) and the Send-ETH flow are not yet wired." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "دعم Ethereum + ERC-20 ضمن خارطة الطريق. يتعامل Maknoon بالفعل مع بيانات اعتماد walletControlEth الخاصة بـ Sandwich الهوية، لكن محفظة السلسلة للقراءة فقط (الرصيد + سجل المعاملات) وتدفق إرسال ETH لم يتم توصيلهما بعد."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ethereum + ERC-20 support is on the roadmap. Maknoon already handles the Identity Sandwich's walletControlEth credential, but the read-only chain wallet (balance + tx history) and the Send-ETH flow are not yet wired."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Ethereum 与 ERC-20 支持已列入路线图。Maknoon 已能处理身份三明治的 walletControlEth 凭据，但只读链上钱包（余额与交易历史）以及发送 ETH 的流程尚未接入。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
