    "Hardware attestation binds a secp256k1 device key (Trezor / Ledger) to your post-quantum master. Real BLE clients ship in a follow-up; the demo path uses a deterministic mock so the wire-format and verifier-check pipeline are exercised end-to-end." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "تشهد الأجهزة بربط مفتاح جهاز secp256k1 (Trezor / Ledger) بمفتاحك الرئيسي ما بعد الكمي. يتم إطلاق عملاء BLE الحقيقيين في تحديث لاحق، ويستخدم مسار العرض التوضيحي محاكاة حتمية بحيث يتم اختبار تنسيق السلك وأنبوب فحص المحقق من البداية إلى النهاية."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Hardware attestation binds a secp256k1 device key (Trezor / Ledger) to your post-quantum master. Real BLE clients ship in a follow-up; the demo path uses a deterministic mock so the wire-format and verifier-check pipeline are exercised end-to-end."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "硬件证明将 secp256k1 设备密钥（Trezor / Ledger）绑定到您的后量子主密钥。真正的 BLE 客户端将在后续版本中发布；演示路径使用确定性 mock，使消息格式与验证方校验流水线得以端到端运行。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hardware Ethereum wallets are added from Settings > Devices once the device is registered. Phase 1 supports registering + reading; Phase 2 adds Ledger SIGN_TRANSACTION for sending." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "تُضاف محافظ Ethereum المادية من الإعدادات > الأجهزة بمجرد تسجيل الجهاز. المرحلة 1 تدعم التسجيل والقراءة، والمرحلة 2 تضيف Ledger SIGN_TRANSACTION للإرسال."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Hardware Ethereum wallets are added from Settings > Devices once the device is registered. Phase 1 supports registering + reading; Phase 2 adds Ledger SIGN_TRANSACTION for sending."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "设备注册后，可在“设置 > 设备”中添加硬件 Ethereum 钱包。第一阶段支持注册与读取；第二阶段将加入 Ledger SIGN_TRANSACTION 用于发送。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
