    "HTML explorer that the Addresses + Transactions screens link out to. Leave blank to mirror the mempool URL above. Point at a local mempool.space install (e.g. http://192.168.1.10:8999) or any explorer that serves /address/<bech32> and /tx/<txid> pages." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
