    "Lets you bump the fee later if the transaction gets stuck in the mempool. Industry default is ON; disable only if your recipient has explicitly asked for a non-RBF transaction." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "يتيح لك زيادة الرسوم لاحقاً إذا علقت المعاملة في mempool. الإعداد الافتراضي في الصناعة هو التفعيل، وعطّله فقط إذا طلب المستلم صراحة معاملة بدون RBF."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lets you bump the fee later if the transaction gets stuck in the mempool. Industry default is ON; disable only if your recipient has explicitly asked for a non-RBF transaction."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "若交易卡在内存池中，可让您后续提升手续费。行业默认为开启；仅在收款人明确要求非 RBF 交易时才关闭。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
