    "Lightning passwords live in Keychain. Account metadata (label, server, username) is included in the YAML settings backup; passwords are NOT exported." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "تعيش كلمات مرور Lightning في Keychain. تُضمَّن بيانات الحساب الوصفية (التسمية، الخادم، اسم المستخدم) في النسخة الاحتياطية لإعدادات YAML، لكن كلمات المرور لا تُصدَّر."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lightning passwords live in Keychain. Account metadata (label, server, username) is included in the YAML settings backup; passwords are NOT exported."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Lightning 密码保存在 Keychain 中。账户元数据（标签、服务器、用户名）会包含在 YAML 设置备份中，但密码不会导出。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Lightning support lands as a custodial integration with a third-party provider (Strike, Wallet of Satoshi, similar). Maknoon will not run a non-custodial Lightning node on-device." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "يصل دعم Lightning كتكامل بحراسة مع مزود خارجي (Strike، Wallet of Satoshi، أو ما شابه). لن يشغّل Maknoon عقدة Lightning غير محروسة على الجهاز."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
