    "Logs capture recent errors, BLE events, RPC failures, and identity-wrap activity to make support easier. They live only in this app's memory until you share or clear them." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "تلتقط السجلات الأخطاء الأخيرة وأحداث BLE وحالات فشل RPC ونشاط تغليف الهوية لتسهيل الدعم. تعيش فقط في ذاكرة هذا التطبيق حتى تشاركها أو تمسحها."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Logs capture recent errors, BLE events, RPC failures, and identity-wrap activity to make support easier. They live only in this app's memory until you share or clear them."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "日志记录近期的错误、BLE 事件、RPC 失败和身份封装活动，便于技术支持。日志只保存在本应用内存中，直到您主动分享或清除。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Logs DO NOT contain your recovery phrase, passphrase, private keys, or wrap keys — those never leave Keychain.\n\nLogs DO contain public-but-identifying information: wallet addresses, transaction hashes, the chains and services you've used, BLE device identifiers, and timestamps. Anyone who reads the logs can correlate your activity on-chain. Only share with people you trust." : {

