    },
    "Maknoon supports many networks, and even anchors temporary verified credentials on some of them. For holding value, though, we only recommend Bitcoin: it is the only cryptocurrency proven as a long-term store of value. Start with a software Bitcoin wallet, or connect a hardware wallet for cold storage." : {

    },
    "Maknoon talks to these services out of the box. You can override any of them with your own endpoint in Settings → Networks." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "يتحدث Maknoon مع هذه الخدمات بشكل افتراضي. يمكنك تجاوز أي منها بنقطة نهاية خاصة بك من الإعدادات ← الشبكات."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Maknoon talks to these services out of the box. You can override any of them with your own endpoint in Settings → Networks."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Maknoon 默认会与这些服务通信。您可以在“设置 → 网络”中用自己的端点替换其中任意一项。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Maknoon will connect over %@, read the device's stable serial, and record it. The device does not need to be promoted into Identity or any network yet." : {

    },
    "Maknoon will connect to the device over Bluetooth, send the PSBT for signing, then broadcast the signed transaction. Make sure the Bitcoin app is open on the device and Bluetooth is enabled." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "سيتصل Maknoon بالجهاز عبر Bluetooth، ويرسل PSBT للتوقيع، ثم يبث المعاملة الموقعة. تأكد من فتح تطبيق Bitcoin على الجهاز وتفعيل Bluetooth."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Maknoon will connect to the device over Bluetooth, send the PSBT for signing, then broadcast the signed transaction. Make sure the Bitcoin app is open on the device and Bluetooth is enabled."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Maknoon 将通过蓝牙连接设备、发送 PSBT 进行签名，并广播已签名的交易。请确保设备上已打开 Bitcoin 应用且蓝牙已启用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Maknoon will walk BIP44 accounts on this device + network until %@ consecutive empty accounts are found, then stop. Each account is a full Electrum scan and can take several seconds." : {

