          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pickup URLs from these hosts are accepted silently. Other hosts trigger a one-time-trust prompt at Receive time. Paste a full URL or just a hostname; only the host is stored." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "تُقبَل عناوين URL للاستلام من هذه المضيفين بصمت. تستدعي المضيفات الأخرى مطالبة ثقة لمرة واحدة عند الاستلام. الصق عنوان URL كاملاً أو اسم مضيف فقط، يُخزَّن المضيف فقط."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pickup URLs from these hosts are accepted silently. Other hosts trigger a one-time-trust prompt at Receive time. Paste a full URL or just a hostname; only the host is stored."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "来自这些主机的领取 URL 将静默接受。其他主机会在接收时触发一次性信任提示。可粘贴完整 URL 或仅主机名，只有主机名会被保存。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pickup URLs from these hosts are accepted silently. Other hosts trigger a one-time-trust prompt at Receive time. Paste a full URL or just a hostname; only the host is stored. The shield turns green only when the issuer is reachable over a valid TLS connection and returns a valid issuer document; pull down to re-check." : {

    },
    "Pickup URLs from trusted issuers fetch silently. Unknown hosts will ask for one-time trust before any network call. Manage the trusted list under Settings → Identity." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "تُجلَب عناوين URL للاستلام من المصدرين الموثوقين بصمت. تطلب المضيفات غير المعروفة ثقة لمرة واحدة قبل أي مكالمة شبكة. أدر القائمة الموثوقة من الإعدادات ← الهوية."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pickup URLs from trusted issuers fetch silently. Unknown hosts will ask for one-time trust before any network call. Manage the trusted list under Settings → Identity."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "来自可信发行方的领取 URL 将静默获取。未知主机会在任何网络调用前请求一次性信任。可在“设置 → 身份”中管理信任列表。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
