            "value" : "Plug a YubiKey 5C into the iPhone's USB-C port. Approve the accessory prompt iOS shows the first time you connect it. Maknoon reads the key's serial number; if the YubiKey is PIN-protected you'll be asked for the PIN."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
