    },
    "Removes the device from Maknoon. Wallets created from this device on any network stay in the wallet list (you can still see them in watch-only mode), but signing on those wallets fails until you re-register the device." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "يزيل الجهاز من Maknoon. تبقى المحافظ المنشأة من هذا الجهاز على أي شبكة في قائمة المحافظ (لا يزال يمكنك رؤيتها في وضع المراقبة فقط)، لكن التوقيع على تلك المحافظ يفشل حتى تعيد تسجيل الجهاز."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Removes the device from Maknoon. Wallets created from this device on any network stay in the wallet list (you can still see them in watch-only mode), but signing on those wallets fails until you re-register the device."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "将此设备从 Maknoon 中移除。该设备在任意网络上创建的钱包仍保留在钱包列表中（您仍可在仅观察模式下查看），但在重新注册该设备之前，这些钱包无法签名。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
