        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "已签名的展示已复制到剪贴板。请粘贴到验证方的工具中。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The signing key comes from the active wallet. For software wallets you'll be asked to authorize once; for hardware wallets the signature happens on-device." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "يأتي مفتاح التوقيع من المحفظة النشطة. بالنسبة للمحافظ البرمجية سيُطلب منك التفويض مرة واحدة، وبالنسبة للمحافظ المادية يحدث التوقيع على الجهاز."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The signing key comes from the active wallet. For software wallets you'll be asked to authorize once; for hardware wallets the signature happens on-device."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "签名密钥来自当前活动钱包。对于软件钱包，会请您授权一次；对于硬件钱包，签名将在设备上完成。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The URL should serve a JSON catalog matching Maknoon's appstore schema. Remote fetch is not yet wired; the URL is recorded today so the upcoming fetcher can use it without reconfiguration." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "يجب أن يقدّم عنوان URL كتالوج JSON يطابق مخطط متجر تطبيقات Maknoon. الجلب البعيد غير موصل بعد، يُسجَّل عنوان URL اليوم ليتمكن الجالب القادم من استخدامه دون إعادة تكوين."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The URL should serve a JSON catalog matching Maknoon's appstore schema. Remote fetch is not yet wired; the URL is recorded today so the upcoming fetcher can use it without reconfiguration."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "该 URL 应提供符合 Maknoon 应用商店架构的 JSON 目录。远程获取功能尚未接入；目前先记录该 URL，便于后续抓取功能直接使用而无需重新配置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The URL should serve a JSON dApps catalog matching Maknoon's schema. Maknoon fetches it and renders its entries alongside the built-in catalog." : {

    },
    "The verifier's required fields are pre-selected below. Toggle others if you want to share more." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
