    "This wallet is air-gapped. Maknoon builds the unsigned PSBT (BIP174); you sign it on the device by scanning the QR; the signed PSBT comes back via the device's QR and Maknoon broadcasts." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "هذه المحفظة معزولة عن الشبكة. يبني Maknoon PSBT غير الموقع (BIP174)، وأنت توقعه على الجهاز بفحص رمز QR، ثم يعود PSBT الموقع عبر رمز QR للجهاز ويبثه Maknoon."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This wallet is air-gapped. Maknoon builds the unsigned PSBT (BIP174); you sign it on the device by scanning the QR; the signed PSBT comes back via the device's QR and Maknoon broadcasts."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "此钱包为离线（air-gapped）钱包。Maknoon 构建未签名的 PSBT（BIP174），您在设备上通过扫描二维码完成签名，已签名的 PSBT 通过设备的二维码返回，再由 Maknoon 广播。"
