          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, Maknoon shows fiat-equivalent captions next to native amounts and queries CoinGecko (https://api.coingecko.com) for live spot prices. When off, no reference prices are displayed anywhere and Maknoon never contacts the price oracle. There is no self-hosted spot-price source today." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "عند التفعيل، يعرض Maknoon أوصافاً بما يعادل العملة الورقية بجانب المبالغ الأصلية ويستعلم من CoinGecko (https://api.coingecko.com) للأسعار الفورية المباشرة. عند التعطيل، لا تُعرض أي أسعار مرجعية في أي مكان ولا يتصل Maknoon أبداً بمرجع الأسعار. لا يوجد مصدر سعر فوري ذاتي الاستضافة اليوم."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, Maknoon shows fiat-equivalent captions next to native amounts and queries CoinGecko (https://api.coingecko.com) for live spot prices. When off, no reference prices are displayed anywhere and Maknoon never contacts the price oracle. There is no self-hosted spot-price source today."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "启用后，Maknoon 会在原生金额旁显示法币等值说明，并向 CoinGecko（https://api.coingecko.com）查询实时现货价格。关闭后，任何位置都不会显示参考价格，Maknoon 也不会联系价格预言机。目前没有可自托管的现货价格来源。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, Maknoon shows fiat-equivalent captions next to native amounts. Crypto is priced in USD from CoinGecko (https://api.coingecko.com) and then converted to your display currency using daily USD foreign-exchange rates from open.er-api.com. When off, no reference prices are displayed anywhere and Maknoon contacts neither service. There is no self-hosted spot-price source today." : {

    },
    "When the integration ships, this screen will host the provider API key, the BOLT-11 / BOLT-12 invoice generator endpoint, and the lifetime spending limit." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "عند إطلاق التكامل، ستستضيف هذه الشاشة مفتاح API للمزود، ونقطة نهاية مولد فواتير BOLT-11 / BOLT-12، وحد الإنفاق مدى الحياة."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When the integration ships, this screen will host the provider API key, the BOLT-11 / BOLT-12 invoice generator endpoint, and the lifetime spending limit."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "该集成发布后，此页面将包含提供商 API 密钥、BOLT-11 / BOLT-12 发票生成端点以及终身消费限额。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Where Maknoon pulls recommended fees and block projection. Defaults to mempool.space; a self-hosted Esplora-compatible instance works too." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "من أين يسحب Maknoon الرسوم الموصى بها وتوقع الكتل. الإعداد الافتراضي هو mempool.space، ومثيل ذاتي الاستضافة متوافق مع Esplora يعمل أيضاً."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Where Maknoon pulls recommended fees and block projection. Defaults to mempool.space; a self-hosted Esplora-compatible instance works too."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Maknoon 获取推荐手续费和区块预测的来源。默认使用 mempool.space；自托管的 Esplora 兼容实例也可使用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Wipes everything on this device: Identity Sandwich, every wallet on every chain, every label, every paired hardware device, the address book, ID documents, Lightning accounts, installed dApps, and every UserDefault setting. Equivalent to deleting and reinstalling the app. The only recovery paths are your 24-word phrase or an encrypted backup file." : {

    },
    "Wipes the locked Identity Sandwich, every registered device, every credential, and every chain wallet. After reset you can restore from your 24-word paper seed and re-register your hardware devices. Only do this if every enrolled device is lost." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "يمسح Sandwich الهوية المقفل، وكل جهاز مسجل، وكل بيانات اعتماد، وكل محفظة سلسلة. بعد إعادة التعيين يمكنك الاستعادة من بذرة الورق المكونة من 24 كلمة وإعادة تسجيل أجهزتك المادية. افعل هذا فقط إذا فُقد كل جهاز مسجل."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Wipes the locked Identity Sandwich, every registered device, every credential, and every chain wallet. After reset you can restore from your 24-word paper seed and re-register your hardware devices. Only do this if every enrolled device is lost."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "清除已锁定的身份三明治、所有已注册设备、所有凭据以及所有链上钱包。重置后，您可以使用 24 个纸质助记词恢复并重新注册硬件设备。仅在所有已注册设备都已丢失时执行此操作。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
